data.name: Anuj Kumar Sharma
data.about: What's up guys, Anuj here. Ex Software Engineer at Amazon & Urban Company and a self-taught programmer. I started this channel to teach you all the things I have learned, things I wish I had known sooner, and things to help you along the way. I'll teach you how to learn new Programming languages, help you understand Data Structures and Algorithms, and develop your soft skills. My goal is to provide you the best advice I can through tutorials so that you can crack the dream company you deserve.
